	<!-- Native Collections window. Mirrors EQUI_NativeAchievementWnd.xml's
	     layout and coordinate scheme almost exactly (same panel sizes, same
	     overall window size, same resize/reflow treatment) so
	     collections_window.cpp can reuse achievements_window.cpp's
	     ReflowIfResized nearly verbatim. Two differences: no rewards list
	     (collections have none) — the Items list simply takes the full
	     width where Achievements split Objectives/Rewards — and the
	     Refresh/Check button pair is Refresh/Deposit instead. -->

